sqlViews.name: NHWA Module 1 Subnational correct org unit name
sqlViews.sqlQuery:
SELECT ouparent.shortname as orgunitparent,
   date_part('year', pe.startdate)::text  AS period,
   ou.shortname AS orgunitname,
   dv.value,
   de.uid AS dataelement,
   co.uid AS categoryoptioncombo,
    ou.uid AS orgunit
FROM datavalue dv
     LEFT JOIN dataelement de ON dv.dataelementid = de.dataelementid
     LEFT JOIN organisationunit ou ON dv.sourceid = ou.organisationunitid
     LEFT JOIN period pe ON dv.periodid = pe.periodid
     LEFT JOIN categoryoptioncombo co ON dv.categoryoptioncomboid = co.categoryoptioncomboid
 LEFT JOIN organisationunit ouparent ON ou.parentid = ouparent.organisationunitid
  WHERE (ou.uid IN ( SELECT ou_1.uid
           FROM dataset ds
             LEFT JOIN datasetsource dss ON ds.datasetid = dss.datasetid
             LEFT JOIN organisationunit ou_1 ON dss.sourceid = ou_1.organisationunitid
          WHERE ds.uid = 'Humg4HbkmJg'))  and de.uid = 'ZUCnSGgjlrw' and value != ou.shortname;
sqlViews.displayName: NHWA Module 1 Subnational correct org unit name
